ar area\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Close-up of cabinetry in bar area; a warming drawer, oven and microwave are&lt;br /&gt; hidden away in these cabinets.&lt;/p&gt; \" data-medium-file=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.atlantavoices.com/dh2/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/IMG_2655-e1485438902346.jpg?fit=400%2C267\" data-large-file=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.atlantavoices.com/dh2/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/IMG_2655-e1485438902346.jpg?fit=980%2C654\" src=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.atlantavoices.com/dh2/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/IMG_2655-e1485438902346.jpg?w=650&#038;h=433\" width=\"650\" height=\"433\" data-original-width=\"650\" data-original-height=\"433\" itemprop=\"http://schema.org/image\" title=\"Close-up of cabinetry in bar area\" alt=\"Close-up of cabinetry in bar area; a warming drawer, oven and microwave are hidden away in these cabinets.\" style=\"width: 650px; height: 433px;\" /> </a> <div class=\"tiled-gallery-caption\" itemprop=\"caption description\"> Close-up of cabinetry in bar area; a warming drawer, oven and microwave are hidden away in these cabinets. </div> </div> </div> <!-- close group --> <div class=\"gallery-group images-2\" style=\"width: 326px; height: 437px;\" data-original-width=\"326\" data-original-height=\"437\" > <div class=\"tiled-gallery-item tiled-gallery-item-large\" itemprop=\"associatedMedia\" itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\"> <a href=\"http://www.atlantavoices.com/dh2/project/project-36/img_2661-2/\" border=\"0\" itemprop=\"url\"> <meta itemprop=\"width\" content=\"322\"> <meta itemprop=\"height\" content=\"215\"> <img data-attachment-id=\"1224\" data-orig-file=\"http://www.atlantavoices.com/dh2/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/IMG_2661-e1485439396500.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1972,1315\" data-comments-opened=\"\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;4.5&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS 6D&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1481635528&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;24&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;12800&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.01&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Living room with shelving built by Dark Horse\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Living room with shelving built by Dark Horse&lt;/p&gt; \" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.atlantavoices.com/dh2/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/IMG_2661-e1485439396500.jpg?fit=400%2C267\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.atlantavoices.com/dh2/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/IMG_2661-e1485439396500.jpg?fit=980%2C654\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.atlantavoices.com/dh2/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/IMG_2661-e1485439396500.jpg?w=322&#038;h=215\" width=\"322\" height=\"215\" data-original-width=\"322\" data-original-height=\"215\" itemprop=\"http://schema.org/image\" title=\"Living room with shelving built by Dark Horse\" alt=\"Living room with shelving built by Dark Horse\" style=\"width: 322px; height: 215px;\" /> </a> <div class=\"tiled-gallery-caption\" itemprop=\"caption description\"> Living room with shelving built by Dark Horse </div> </div> <div class=\"tiled-gallery-item tiled-gallery-item-large\" itemprop=\"associatedMedia\" itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\"> <a href=\"http://www.atlantavoices.com/dh2/project/project-36/img_2646/\" border=\"0\" itemprop=\"url\"> <meta itemprop=\"width\" content=\"322\"> <meta itemprop=\"height\" content=\"214\"> <img data-attachment-id=\"1227\" data-orig-file=\"http://www.atlantavoices.com/dh2/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/IMG_2646.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"5472,3648\" data-comments-opened=\"\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;4&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS 6D&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1481635256&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;24&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;5000&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.033333333333333&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Wide view of the bar\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Wide view of the bar.&lt;/p&gt; \" data-medium-file=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.atlantavoices.com/dh2/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/IMG_2646.jpg?fit=400%2C267\" data-large-file=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.atlantavoices.com/dh2/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/IMG_2646.jpg?fit=980%2C654\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.atlantavoices.com/dh2/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/IMG_2646.jpg?w=322&#038;h=214\" width=\"322\" height=\"214\" data-original-width=\"322\" data-original-height=\"214\" itemprop=\"http://schema.org/image\" title=\"Wide view of the bar\" alt=\"Wide view of the bar.\" style=\"width: 322px; height: 214px;\" /> </a> <div class=\"tiled-gallery-caption\" itemprop=\"caption description\"> Wide view of the bar. </div> </div> </div> <!-- close group --> </div> <!-- close row --> </div>\n<p><strong>Word of mouth matters</strong></p>\n<p>It’s always gratifying when someone sees our past work and gets in touch based on how much they liked it. Our client was attending an event and saw our Wesley project, an extensive, grain-matched bar that is modeled on a hotel bar in LA.</p>\n<p><strong>Cabinetry way beyond the kitchen</strong></p>\n<p>We spent about two months on our part of this impressive basement renovation project.</p>\n<p>We created the main bar, living room shelving, a hidden cabinet for the game area and cabinetry for the guest bath, powder room, gentleman’s lounge and wine vestibule.</p>\n<p>The cabinetry in the bar area includes a hidden-away warming drawer, oven and microwave; all appliances are Wolf or Sub-zero.</p>\n<p>Walnut was used for much of the shelving and cabinetry; the one special request from the client was that we match the color of the existing trim, as well as the floor in two areas of the basement.</p>\n<p>My favorite part of the project was the living room shelving with recessed lighting – it is 12 feet high and fits the space perfectly.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_1224\" style=\"width: 1982px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.atlantavoices.com/dh2/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/IMG_2661-e1485439396500.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1224\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1224\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.atlantavoices.com/dh2/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/IMG_2661-e1485439396500.jpg?resize=980%2C653\" alt=\"\" width=\"980\" height=\"653\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-1224\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Living room with shelving built by Dark Horse</p></div>\n<p>As always, we’re grateful that such great work comes our way.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_1222\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><a href=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.atlantavoices.com/dh2/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/IMG_2650-e1485439129399.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1222\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-1222\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.atlantavoices.com/dh2/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/IMG_2650.jpg?resize=400%2C267\" alt=\"Gaming area with lift-out storage hidden…\" width=\"400\" height=\"267\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-1222\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Gaming area with lift-out storage hidden…</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_1221\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption alignright\"><a href=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.atlantavoices.com/dh2/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/IMG_2649-e1485439213467.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1221\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-1221\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.atlantavoices.com/dh2/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/IMG_2649.jpg?resize=400%2C267\" alt=\"Gaming area with lift-out storage revealed\" width=\"400\" height=\"267\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-1221\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">And revealed.</p></div>\n<div class=\"sharedaddy sd-sharing-enable